        "content": "<p>wasmtime-publish opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13277\">PR #13277</a> from <code>bytecodealliance:ci/bump-to-46.0.0</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This is an [automated pull request][process] from CI which indicates that the next [<code>release-45.0.0</code> branch][branch] has been created and the <code>main</code> branch is getting its version number bumped from 45.0.0 to 46.0.0.</p>\n<p>Maintainers should take a moment to review the [release notes][RELEASES.md] for 45.0.0 and any updates should be made directly to the [release branch][branch].</p>\n<p>Another automated PR will be made in roughly 2 weeks time when for the actual release itself.</p>\n<p>If any issues arise on the <code>main</code> branch before the release is made then the issue should first be fixed on <code>main</code> and then backport to the <code>release-45.0.0</code> branch.</p>\n<p>[RELEASES.md]: <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/release-45.0.0/RELEASES.md\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/release-45.0.0/RELEASES.md</a><br>\n[branch]: <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/tree/release-45.0.0\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/tree/release-45.0.0</a><br>\n[process]: <a href=\"https://docs.wasmtime.dev/contributing-release-process.html\">https://docs.wasmtime.dev/contributing-release-process.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
